property_deets <- property_deets |> 
mutate(
    latitude = as.numeric(str_extract(centroid, "\\((.+),", group = 1)),
    longitude = as.numeric(str_extract(centroid, ",(.+)\\)", group = 1))
    )
property_deets
property_deets_geo <- st_as_sf(property_deets |> 
  drop_na(latitude), 
  coords = c('longitude', 'latitude'),
  crs = st_crs(radius))
